{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set during the height of the Cold War, You Left Us is a first-person psychological horror game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Award-Winning Tension</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crowned the victor of Pirate Software Game Jam 14, You Left Us promises a heart-pounding journey through the depths of psychological horror. As you peel back the layers of this meticulously crafted narrative, every decision, every moment of silence, draws you deeper into a world where trust is a luxury, and survival a precarious game of cat and mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the void of the cold unknown, where the only thing more uncertain than your allies is your chance of escape. Welcome to You Left Us, where silence speaks volumes and the darkness hides more than just secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866730/extras/firecunt1-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1730166362\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Pressure Is Rising</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As tensions simmer on the global stage, you are tasked with eavesdropping on the world's superpowers from the isolation of a remote Arctic listening post.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866730/extras/fire1-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1730166362\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Eavesdrop, Explore, and Upkeep the Base</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>While Manning Your Listening Post</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tune into foreign power's frequencies to gather information</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick up key items to help you complete your objective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fuel the furnaces and maintain the generators to stave off the darkness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover secrets hidden within the base</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866730/extras/YLU_ShadowMonster.gif?t=1730166362\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unravel the Mystery</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel the anxiety grip your heart as anomalies ripple across the globe. Could the Russians be orchestrating these disturbances? Perhaps the Americans? Delve into a web of intrigue as you seek to unravel the truth, testing the limits of your wit and will to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866730/extras/map1-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1730166362\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome Aboard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/33aebf38b68bf78d262d685a594b17f969a0ff0a.jpg"},{"name":"Energized","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/13d5342b5fc18344f2ef1cbc095d5879318f546a.jpg"},{"name":"Origin Unknown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/d9d718d647e7265f4ebaf84583d32eee142c810b.jpg"},{"name":"Be Home Soon...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/402f20dad0ac487a0a096575226026d3388ef792.jpg"},{"name":"Tape Found","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/2fbfbe2a8b8096c722bf9221c7ce72d2574c16ab.jpg"},{"name":"All Tapes Found","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2866730/0